Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Bohol National High School in the City of Tagbilaran to Dr. Cecilio Putong National High School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 341
An Act Changing the Name of the Bohol National High School in the City of Tagbilaran to Dr. Cecilio Putong National High School
Section 1. The name of the Bohol National High School in the City of Tagbilaran is changed to Dr. Cecilio Putong National High School.1awp++i1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: February 25, 1983
